div.span:
1. Build Agent in Copilot Studio
Create mission, prompts, workflows, actions
Prepare test cases and documentation
Maker only - no admin needed

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span:
2. Configure Knowledge & Connectors
List data sources: SharePoint, Exchange,
Teams, Dataverse, external APIs
Map OAuth scopes and permissions

div.style: display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;
display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
Prepare tenant consent request
& security documentation

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span:
3. Test in Sandbox
Run scenarios, adaptive cards, workflows
Log failures and fix
Maker only - no admin needed

div.style: display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;
display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;

span.p:
Personal/Draft Publish
- For self only
- Cannot share org-wide
- No admin approval
- Tenant consent connectors blocked

div.style: color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important; display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;
display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
Org Publish/Agent Store/
Teams/M365 Copilot
Submit package + docs +
connector consent requests

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span:
5. Admin Review
Check: connector scopes, data handling,
conditional access, channel enablement,
legal/compliance

div.style: display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;
display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
Admin Actions:
- Enable channel
- Grant tenant consent
- Deploy to Teams/Copilot
- Notify maker
- Enable monitoring

div.style: display: table; white-space: break-spaces; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center; width: 200px;
div.span:
7. Post-Publish Operations
- Monitoring & telemetry
- Change control
- Updates adding scopes = re-approval
- Admin can revoke/restrict centrally

div.style: display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;

span.p:
Admin Returns Rejection:
- Security concerns
- Excessive scopes
- Missing documentation

div.style: display: table-cell; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 1.5; max-width: 200px; text-align: center;
div.span:
6. Maker Remediation
- Narrow scopes
- Add documentation
- Replace risky APIs
- Re-test
